  "$id": "https://taxat.dev/schemas/authority_ingress_proof_contract.schema.json",
  "title": "AuthorityIngressProofContract",
  "description": "Shared authenticated ingress proof contract. This schema freezes the provider-channel authentication evidence, deterministic delivery dedupe identity, canonical_delivery_key semantics, request-lineage binding basis, lineage_binding_hash semantics, canonical ingress receipt anchor, and mutation gate that must remain attributable from ingress checkpoint through normalized response and any authority-backed truth mutation.",
